			<div class="content" id="post-content-1597951">
									

<p>Not at all, really<br />
Just as the Foundation is not the almighty repository for all things paranormal-related, its enemies are not the four horsemen of the apocalypse, and they do have a point: most humanoid SCPs are well, HUMANS with FEELINGS and all that jazz, so, you know, keeping them in a cell just because they can travel through pictures or some shit like that is really cruel, but that's what the Big F does: Secure, Contain and Protect</p>
<p>Actually, if I was given a choice in real-life, I'd probably join AWCY? because motherfucking <em>art on a whole new level</em>, man</p>
<p>(What if I started calling the Foundation &quot;the Big F&quot; from now on [How To Get Banned In A Single Post By SCP Forum User Tiefling])</p>

